see the person's contact information then select the displayed information and copy it to your clipboard it can then be pasted in an email or other document without special formatting last modified mon 29 nov 2010 at 10 42 pages about this service overview searching stanfordwho directory details linking to stanfordwho results advanced stanfordwho features find answers submit a helpsu request stanford answers related pages directory service footer links stanford university helpsu user login stanford university terms of use copyright complaints
